{"tid":1905500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你果區有驗武肺診所，患者2日從社區隔離；你果區無，係社區播12日毒先入院隔離。","createTime":"2020-03-01T09:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T14:33:32.000Z","uid":38255,"like":11,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a652c5278757bb5f772012e0a8b464635a33e106","tid":1905500,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T09:53:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她於 <span style=\"color: red;\">2 月 12 日</span> 出現咳嗽，並數次向同一名私家醫生求醫。她於 <span style=\"color: red;\">2 月 24 日</span>入住養和醫院，於 2 月 25 日轉往瑪麗醫院接受隔離治療。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>患者有長期病患，獨居於北角錦屏街 40-78 號鴻福大樓。她自 <span style=\"color: red;\">2 月 25 日</span>出現間歇咳嗽，2 月 26 日到柏立基夫人普通科門診診所求醫，<span style=\"color: red;\">2 月 27 日</span>患者的深喉唾液樣本呈陽性反應，獲安排往伊利沙伯醫院入院接受治療。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你話要諮詢要監察我明，但話自己果區唔要有係咪同隔離營撈亂左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你果區無先仲大機會社區爆發喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無武肺診所唔會就無武肺病人，但無驗得既診所咪頻頻撲撲睇幾次私家係個社區播多十日毒先入院隔離囉，唔係仲大風險咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前已經開左個post，但標題唔太吸引開過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果有適當諮詢同監測，其實係應該十八甚至二十區都有指定武肺診所先啱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1905355\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1905355</a>"},{"pid":"b5f727f6029b1fa3d58c16fe872d33c1d06bfe1a","tid":1905500,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T09:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228ec3e7dd5259bb1a342567ffdd9f4c0cd98686","tid":1905500,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"個重點幾時由封關/唔封關變成有隔離中心/冇隔離中心？"},{"pid":"e7ba0ba721a0061b2a999f59cbedf456c07683e6","tid":1905500,"uid":47905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"重點係你講野1999<br />\n所以先無人理<br />\n<br />\n睇左3次先GET到你講乜<br />\n<br />\n爸打要學下點樣講重點 點樣簡化<br />\n點樣令到人輕鬆睇到你想講既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541b1e99ef70dcb16234ca1c25c77ee61851509a","tid":1905500,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c65a0fa51110ce9e9b1462bf89a68c5cdfec0a6","tid":1905500,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"唔關事,依家所有診所有相關徵狀就叫你抽口水拎去驗"},{"pid":"f8d619d55ea787138b2487f6ad9f225baa8738e2","tid":1905500,"uid":88743,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c65a0fa51110ce9e9b1462bf89a68c5cdfec0a6","tid":1905500,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"唔關事,依家所有診所有相關徵狀就叫你抽口水拎去驗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"條友偷換概念<br />\n求其俾兩個確診例子就當係"},{"pid":"8c9db5ca03aae83b7715d16654f4b0f71c08f624","tid":1905500,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c65a0fa51110ce9e9b1462bf89a68c5cdfec0a6","tid":1905500,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:16:51.000Z","msg":"唔關事,依家所有診所有相關徵狀就叫你抽口水拎去驗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-01T10:23:42.000Z","msg":"患者於 2 月 13 日有咳嗽及痰，向私家醫生求醫，直至 2 月 23 日沒有好轉再求診。患者得知「福慧精舍」佛堂有確診個案後，致電衛生防護中心熱線，其後被送往聯合醫院。<br />\n<br />\n我記得2月8號起已經有自己抽深喉樣本去驗呢個計劃，但13號睇私家都無得驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁如果係所有政府普通科門診所都有得驗，咁非指定診所既風險其實同指定診所差幾遠呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abf0f50135b5eafed0864502a1fb90a1cf9c1e4a","tid":1905500,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c9db5ca03aae83b7715d16654f4b0f71c08f624","tid":1905500,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c65a0fa51110ce9e9b1462bf89a68c5cdfec0a6","tid":1905500,"uid":17646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit